      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i don't really want to go back to the clinic if i don't have to, it's such a hassle. you're pretty sure the yellow stuff is just part of the healing? i was thinking of maybe putting a bit more of the antibiotic cream on it thicker so it stays covered up, would that be better?",
