      "content": "okay good, that makes me feel better. i have some old ibuprofen in my cabinet from a few months ago, can i take a couple of those to help with the warmth and any potential inflammation? also do you think i should try to wrap it in some gauze to keep the cream from rubbing off on my clothes?",
